    <string name="workout_explanation_message">🏃‍♂️ <b>Why are the numbers different from your fitness app?</b>\n\n📱 <b>Your Fitness App Shows:</b> Total calories burned during workout\n\n🍎 <b>CalorieTracker Shows:</b> 70% of those calories as bonus\n\n❓ <b>Why only 70%?</b>\nResearch shows that eating back 100% of workout calories can prevent weight loss. CalorieTracker uses 70% to:\n\n• Account for estimation errors in fitness trackers\n• Maintain a healthy calorie deficit\n• Support sustainable weight management\n\n💡 <b>Example:</b>\n• Fitness app: 1425 calories burned\n• CalorieTracker bonus: 997 calories (70%)\n• Added to your daily goal for healthy fuel!</string>
